Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.97,0:00:03.61,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,轻轻摇动的死亡之影
Dialogue: 0,0:00:04.37,0:00:06.74,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,悲惨的命运 迷失的道路
Dialogue: 0,0:00:07.25,0:00:09.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,憎恨与被憎恨之间产生的裂缝
Dialogue: 0,0:00:09.75,0:00:12.03,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有如双面镜般的双生茧
Dialogue: 0,0:00:12.96,0:00:14.95,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,从时间混杂的黑暗中走来
Dialogue: 0,0:00:15.44,0:00:18.31,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你的怨恨 我来消除
Dialogue: 0,0:01:53.61,0:02:01.34,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,吾已闻汝之恨…
Dialogue: 0,0:02:04.29,0:02:05.47,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,难道说你…
Dialogue: 0,0:02:17.36,0:02:18.79,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,都是你那个地狱通信害的
Dialogue: 0,0:02:19.27,0:02:21.05,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有人被怀疑被伤害了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:02:21.50,0:02:22.42,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,马上住手吧
Dialogue: 0,0:02:23.86,0:02:26.58,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这不是我能决定的事情
Dialogue: 0,0:02:27.37,0:02:32.12,题名,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,彷徨
Dialogue: 0,0:02:45.99,0:02:46.99,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这里是…
Dialogue: 0,0:02:54.11,0:02:54.88,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,拓真
Dialogue: 0,0:03:10.85,0:03:14.51,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,露木先生 这个人真的是拓真的同伙吗
Dialogue: 0,0:03:15.90,0:03:16.77,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没错
Dialogue: 0,0:03:17.79,0:03:20.47,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对其放任不管的话 我们就危险了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:24.57,0:03:26.81,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因为你用了地狱通信才会这样的
Dialogue: 0,0:03:27.65,0:03:28.77,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你在说什么啊
Dialogue: 0,0:03:29.16,0:03:31.32,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,说到底 还不是为了你才这么做的
Dialogue: 0,0:03:32.36,0:03:35.95,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,莲江 你也早就是我们的共犯了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:36.45,0:03:37.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是啊
Dialogue: 0,0:03:39.01,0:03:42.04,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我们可不会让你一个人逃掉的
Dialogue: 0,0:03:47.13,0:03:49.54,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,已经开始组建奇怪的党派了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:50.75,0:03:54.08,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那样的人只有死路一条了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:06.14,0:04:06.77,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,人在吗
Dialogue: 0,0:04:07.25,0:04:08.95,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没有 家中已经没人了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:09.52,0:04:10.04,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可恶
Dialogue: 0,0:04:15.27,0:04:16.01,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,发生什么事情了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:17.17,0:04:19.75,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么办啊 也不知道哥哥在哪里
Dialogue: 0,0:04:30.76,0:04:31.52,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,拓真
Dialogue: 0,0:04:45.73,0:04:46.83,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,姐姐 要去哪里啊
Dialogue: 0,0:04:47.36,0:04:48.08,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,等会再说
Dialogue: 0,0:04:54.52,0:04:54.94,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,进来
Dialogue: 0,0:04:57.72,0:04:59.79,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没事吧 哪里受伤了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:05:01.13,0:05:02.72,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为什么要来救我
Dialogue: 0,0:05:03.83,0:05:05.87,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,错不在你 都怪阎魔爱
Dialogue: 0,0:05:06.66,0:05:08.29,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就是因为有地狱通信这种东西在
Dialogue: 0,0:05:08.74,0:05:09.95,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大家才会变得奇怪的
Dialogue: 0,0:05:11.13,0:05:12.56,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你相信了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:05:14.11,0:05:15.07,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我看到了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:17.23,0:05:17.85,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,总之
Dialogue: 0,0:05:18.27,0:05:20.45,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,必须要告诉哥哥澄清你是无辜的
Dialogue: 0,0:05:20.87,0:05:21.83,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那…那个
Dialogue: 0,0:05:24.48,0:05:25.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不行啊 没人接
Dialogue: 0,0:05:31.99,0:05:32.97,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,萤 怎么了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:34.85,0:05:38.52,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你哥哥？没看到啊
Dialogue: 0,0:05:39.98,0:05:40.71,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我知道了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:40.98,0:05:42.19,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那再去问问其他人好了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:42.96,0:05:43.57,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我说你啊
Dialogue: 0,0:05:44.39,0:05:45.88,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,做什么啊慢腾腾的
Dialogue: 0,0:05:46.17,0:05:46.99,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,快给我过来
Dialogue: 0,0:05:47.66,0:05:49.13,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不好意思 一会再说 再见了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:49.90,0:05:51.07,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对不起 我这就过去
Dialogue: 0,0:05:52.89,0:05:53.75,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真迟钝
Dialogue: 0,0:06:06.27,0:06:08.86,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,吾已闻汝之恨
Dialogue: 0,0:06:32.15,0:06:37.26,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哥哥已经调查过了 地狱少女的事情
Dialogue: 0,0:06:40.12,0:06:40.52,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,姐姐
Dialogue: 0,0:06:42.50,0:06:43.75,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那位刑警先生
Dialogue: 0,0:06:46.01,0:06:47.17,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,被人带走了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:49.49,0:06:52.15,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以在这呆着的话会有危险的
Dialogue: 0,0:07:04.55,0:07:04.93,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要跳了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:06.22,0:07:06.61,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,看着
Dialogue: 0,0:07:09.43,0:07:09.76,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,来吧
Dialogue: 0,0:07:11.31,0:07:11.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是
Dialogue: 0,0:07:12.56,0:07:14.43,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没关系的 快点
Dialogue: 0,0:07:20.39,0:07:21.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,做得很好
Dialogue: 0,0:07:23.24,0:07:24.58,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,发现了 在这边
Dialogue: 0,0:07:41.54,0:07:42.26,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,已经没事了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:42.98,0:07:43.87,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这里很安全的
Dialogue: 0,0:07:44.99,0:07:49.13,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小学捉迷藏的时候我经常躲在这里
Dialogue: 0,0:07:49.97,0:07:51.93,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,每次到最后都没人能找到我
Dialogue: 0,0:07:53.37,0:07:55.61,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不会害怕吗 一个人
Dialogue: 0,0:07:57.88,0:07:59.41,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我很害怕
Dialogue: 0,0:08:05.07,0:08:07.23,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我不会让你孤单一人的
Dialogue: 0,0:08:10.41,0:08:11.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我不明白了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:13.41,0:08:15.13,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我也许是真正的恶魔之子
Dialogue: 0,0:08:16.40,0:08:19.26,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以周围的人都会因为我而不幸
Dialogue: 0,0:08:20.04,0:08:22.85,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没有这种事 没有这种事的
Dialogue: 0,0:08:30.19,0:08:32.58,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你没有使用过地狱通信
Dialogue: 0,0:08:33.15,0:08:34.87,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也没有把谁流放到地狱去
Dialogue: 0,0:08:35.76,0:08:37.49,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,绝对不是什么恶魔之子
Dialogue: 0,0:08:38.95,0:08:39.56,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真的吗
Dialogue: 0,0:08:40.25,0:08:40.94,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真的
Dialogue: 0,0:08:41.99,0:08:43.34,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哥哥也一定这么认为
Dialogue: 0,0:08:44.74,0:08:46.01,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是 他被人袭击了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:47.16,0:08:49.31,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没关系 哥哥很强的
Dialogue: 0,0:08:49.76,0:08:51.01,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不会输给那种家伙
Dialogue: 0,0:08:52.94,0:08:54.57,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一定会来救我们的
Dialogue: 0,0:09:09.71,0:09:12.49,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可恶 那些家伙去哪了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:14.56,0:09:15.69,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,到底以后要怎么做
Dialogue: 0,0:09:16.92,0:09:18.79,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,首先要干掉拓真
Dialogue: 0,0:09:19.25,0:09:19.79,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,干掉？
Dialogue: 0,0:09:21.92,0:09:23.84,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那样的小鬼消失一个也没关系吧
Dialogue: 0,0:09:26.93,0:09:30.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,刑警要怎么办 不能一直这样下去
Dialogue: 0,0:09:31.30,0:09:32.67,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,倒不如干脆就…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:33.39,0:09:34.23,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也是啊
Dialogue: 0,0:09:44.90,0:09:46.11,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这次是轮入道吗
Dialogue: 0,0:09:47.45,0:09:48.84,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,还真是肆意的使用呢
Dialogue: 0,0:09:49.68,0:09:50.68,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这个城市的家伙们
Dialogue: 0,0:10:03.91,0:10:06.75,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,变冷了 再过来点
Dialogue: 0,0:10:11.67,0:10:14.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你父亲能快点恢复健康就好了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:30.95,0:10:31.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,原来是这样啊
Dialogue: 0,0:10:33.00,0:10:36.64,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,地狱少女也受了不少的苦啊
Dialogue: 0,0:10:37.81,0:10:40.98,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,曾经有一个不幸的少女
Dialogue: 0,0:10:43.39,0:10:46.74,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,少女因莫须有的事情被迫害
Dialogue: 0,0:10:49.09,0:10:50.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,住在同一个村子的人们
Dialogue: 0,0:10:52.91,0:10:55.83,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,打着保护村庄的所谓正义的幌子
Dialogue: 0,0:10:56.61,0:10:58.49,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,把少女逼得走投无路
Dialogue: 0,0:11:24.15,0:11:29.41,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,于是 最后少女被愚蠢的村民们抓住
Dialogue: 0,0:11:30.30,0:11:31.82,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,失去了生命
Dialogue: 0,0:11:33.62,0:11:39.43,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那是当时的村子社会中 被称为牺牲的死亡
Dialogue: 0,0:11:50.51,0:11:54.18,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,集体有时会失去心中的理性
Dialogue: 0,0:11:55.55,0:11:59.15,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,像这样 被集体排挤的人的负面心理
Dialogue: 0,0:12:00.48,0:12:02.49,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,即使到现在也没有改变
Dialogue: 0,0:12:06.11,0:12:09.35,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,地狱少女也是孤单一人啊
Dialogue: 0,0:12:12.99,0:12:15.48,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是 那还是个不该存在的东西
Dialogue: 0,0:12:16.37,0:12:17.49,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那个地狱通信
Dialogue: 0,0:12:21.78,0:12:23.69,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你很伤心吗 姐姐
Dialogue: 0,0:12:24.78,0:12:27.47,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是啊 也许是
Dialogue: 0,0:12:29.19,0:12:30.64,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我会保护你
Dialogue: 0,0:12:31.20,0:12:32.04,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一定会
Dialogue: 0,0:12:38.61,0:12:40.88,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好了 稍微休息一下比较好
Dialogue: 0,0:12:55.78,0:12:59.34,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,爱 怎么了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:13:01.18,0:13:03.98,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只是有点累了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:37.98,0:13:38.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,下雪了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:39.83,0:13:41.03,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,姐姐 下雪了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:07.16,0:14:09.18,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他们在这里吗
Dialogue: 0,0:14:12.86,0:14:13.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,别管她了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:14.22,0:14:15.35,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这边的事才是重点
Dialogue: 0,0:14:17.28,0:14:18.01,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,说得也是
Dialogue: 0,0:14:25.08,0:14:26.72,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为什么要做这种事情
Dialogue: 0,0:14:28.23,0:14:29.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不是纪玖理的错
Dialogue: 0,0:14:32.29,0:14:33.17,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这样就好了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:46.00,0:14:46.65,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,找到了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:47.11,0:14:47.65,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,恶魔之子
Dialogue: 0,0:14:48.27,0:14:50.55,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不是的 这个孩子不是恶魔之子
Dialogue: 0,0:14:51.94,0:14:52.59,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,带走
Dialogue: 0,0:15:07.72,0:15:08.42,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,姐姐
Dialogue: 0,0:15:08.95,0:15:10.28,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没事的 没事
Dialogue: 0,0:15:11.84,0:15:12.92,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,愚蠢的家伙们
Dialogue: 0,0:15:14.00,0:15:15.36,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你们打算怎么做
Dialogue: 0,0:15:16.14,0:15:17.59,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,当然是让你们消失了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:19.39,0:15:20.76,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只要你们消失了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:21.41,0:15:23.76,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我们就会恢复原来的生活了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:24.99,0:15:26.71,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你们太碍事了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:27.34,0:15:28.33,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什 什么啊
Dialogue: 0,0:15:28.94,0:15:30.92,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你们做这种事要是被哥哥知道了的话
Dialogue: 0,0:15:31.74,0:15:33.08,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不会放过你们的
Dialogue: 0,0:15:34.90,0:15:35.67,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也是啊
Dialogue: 0,0:15:37.94,0:15:38.84,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好了 上船吧
Dialogue: 0,0:15:40.65,0:15:41.22,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,姐姐
Dialogue: 0,0:15:42.14,0:15:42.96,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你也上去
Dialogue: 0,0:15:48.77,0:15:51.36,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,老公不要慢腾腾的 快动手啊
Dialogue: 0,0:16:03.16,0:16:04.24,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是让人不舒服啊
Dialogue: 0,0:16:17.75,0:16:19.11,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,果然做得有些过分了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:16:19.88,0:16:21.09,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,事到如今 你还在说什么啊
Dialogue: 0,0:16:21.94,0:16:23.76,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是啊 坚定点
Dialogue: 0,0:16:24.53,0:16:26.65,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是 怎么说也不用杀了他们吧
Dialogue: 0,0:16:27.44,0:16:29.63,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,已经迟了 怎么做也没用了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:30.19,0:16:32.03,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是的 只能这么做了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:32.46,0:16:33.79,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你也明白的吧
Dialogue: 0,0:16:35.93,0:16:36.88,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,救救我 哥哥
Dialogue: 0,0:16:38.32,0:16:39.22,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,姐姐
Dialogue: 0,0:16:40.60,0:16:42.03,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好了 快点动手
Dialogue: 0,0:16:51.65,0:16:52.12,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不要
Dialogue: 0,0:16:53.23,0:16:54.02,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不要怪我啊
Dialogue: 0,0:16:58.05,0:17:01.14,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不要啊 救命啊
Dialogue: 0,0:17:02.67,0:17:06.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不要啊 救命啊救命…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:06.40,0:17:07.47,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哥哥救救我
Dialogue: 0,0:17:07.94,0:17:10.62,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,姐姐不要摇啊 会沉下去的
Dialogue: 0,0:17:11.35,0:17:12.66,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,谁来救救我
